{"tid":2487373,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有無人記得以前高登笑IVE 風氣","createTime":"2021-04-13T13:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T13:49:25.000Z","uid":19602,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5c3763417bbedef5f6a871bcc65ff5f0cd264100","tid":2487373,"uid":19602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T13:20:45.000Z","msg":"首先,屌臭asso ive o 既風氣,由4月尾至6月中會達至高峰，<br />\n因為班AL面對放榜壓力無從發洩 <br />\n要搵人黎踩下定下個心 <br />\n6月中後會突然水盡鵝飛 <br />\n一黎怕自己會入，留條後路 <br />\n二黎開始迷信，想積下口德 <br />\n<br />\nAL放榜後，愁雲慘霧 <br />\n班CE仔見狀都唔敢亂屌 <br />\n所以由6月尾至8月 <br />\n情況相若，風氣極低位橫行，如經濟衰退一樣 <br />\n<br />\n到9月，開學兩三禮拜，新一屆AL CE仔開始有壓力，想搵人踩 <br />\nretake緊o既又想有野俾佢增強信心，又踩 <br />\n讀緊asso ive 跟唔上o個班/讀得唔開心o既，又踩 <br />\n因此9月會有個小陽春，之後橫行，<br />\n12月至1月頭，同2月中，分別都會有個小陽春，因為有假放得閒，同考試迫近，<br />\n壓力愈來愈大，3月至4月頭會一直高位橫行 <br />\n<br />\n最後又到4月尾高峰 <br />\n年年都如是，歲歲皆如此 <br />\n<br />\n股市係咁就好囉屌你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRJCqOs0W2xy-_Ai70yBTY0LAZLXANq714dog&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcRJCqOs0W2xy-_Ai70yBTY0LAZLXANq714dog%26usqp%3DCAU&h=f0411ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a833cd101383aba478aadf35ea4d5bf010f9517","tid":2487373,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T13:29:00.000Z","msg":"認真 ive好前途過BU"},{"pid":"6d1fae9cd19fad77640a540217abeda9b2e83d58","tid":2487373,"uid":19602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T13:47:54.000Z","msg":"真係無人笑IVE 了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f87599b099869b3ba53558ebfda211a40404978","tid":2487373,"uid":180401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a833cd101383aba478aadf35ea4d5bf010f9517","tid":2487373,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1